    "The estimates are obtained from a multivariate regression of AI chatbot adoption on worker characteristics X, controlling for occupation fixed effects, and are estimated separately based on employers' AI chatbot initiatives.",
    "All other characteristics are based on register variables from 2022.",
    "Experience is the years of employment in the relevant occupation.",
    "Earnings are total labor income.",
    "Net Wealth is the sum of real assets, financial assets, and pension savings minus the sum of priority debt, other private debt, and public debt, winsorized at the 5th and 95th percentiles."
